[I] The lazier way to manage everything docker

[T] A simple terminal UI for both docker and docker-compose, written in Go with
[T] the gocui library.

[U] https://github.com/jesseduffield/lazydocker

[A] Jesse Duffield
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

[C] extra/tool

[L] MIT
[V] 0.25.0

[D] 91e6ebf86294c44518e75ea9ef7d9648c0419f8f179d3bd1af185ecc lazydocker-0.25.0.tar.gz https://github.com/jesseduffield/lazydocker/archive/v0.25.0/

var_append goconfopt ' ' '-ldflags "-X main.version=$ver"'
hook_add postmake 5 'install lazydocker $root$bindir/'
